  Item 2.02.  Results of Operations and       
              Financial Condition.            
                                              
On July 16, 2020, Morgan Stanley (the
"Company") released financial information with
respect to its quarter ended June 30, 2020. A
copy of the press release containing this
information is annexed as Exhibit 99.1 to this
Report and by this reference incorporated
herein and made a part hereof. In addition, a
copy of the Company's Financial Data
Supplement for its quarter ended June 30, 2020
is annexed as Exhibit 99.2 to this Report and
by this reference incorporated herein and made
a part hereof. The information furnished under
Item 2.02 of this Report, including Exhibit
99.1 and Exhibit 99.2, shall be deemed to be
"filed" for purposes of the Securities
Exchange Act of 1934, as amended.
